WEBVTT

00:11:57.595 --> 00:12:02.345
But as much as we want
the media to change,

00:12:02.369 --> 00:12:06.043
they are for-profit organizations.

00:12:06.706 --> 00:12:11.275
They won't change unless
we hold them accountable.

00:12:12.930 --> 00:12:16.865
(Applause)

00:12:17.354 --> 00:12:20.889
The media makes their money

00:12:20.913 --> 00:12:22.626
from advertising

00:12:22.650 --> 00:12:26.442
based on the number of viewers and clicks.

00:12:26.983 --> 00:12:33.983
If we can reduce the number
of viewers and clicks on any subject,